Playing around with http://code.google.com/p/js-test-driver/


To run these tests start a dev server like this:

java -jar JsTestDriver-1.2.2.jar --port 4224 --browser `which firefox` &

or this:

java -jar JsTestDriver-1.2.2.jar --port 4224 --browser `which google-chrome` &


and run the tests like this:

java -jar JsTestDriver-1.2.2.jar --tests all --reset --testOutput .


or just run this:

java -jar JsTestDriver-1.2.2.jar --port 4224 --browser `which firefox`,`which google-chrome` --tests all
